vu, vu hot ir geboyrn gevorn?

00:02:18.888 --> 00:02:21.144
ikh bin geboyrn gevorn in Poyln,

00:02:21.369 --> 00:02:22.932
in a shtetele Apt,

00:02:23.647 --> 00:02:25.784
dos host zikh gerufn Kongres Poyln.

00:02:25.824 --> 00:02:28.642
vi hot es zikh ongerufn oyf poylish dos shtetl?

00:02:27.528 --> 00:02:28.805
OPATOW.

