lebn velkhe gresere shtot iz dos geven?

00:02:31.105 --> 00:02:35.574
se iz gevezn arum, di gresere shtetlekh zenen geven arum Radom,

00:02:35.594 --> 00:02:39.065
di hoypt shtot fun di VOYEVUTSVE iz gevezn Kelts.

00:02:39.560 --> 00:02:43.486
se iz in di svive fun SANDOMIERZ, OSTROVYETS,

00:02:44.839 --> 00:02:47.553
klenere shtetelekh CMIELOW,

00:02:48.065 --> 00:02:50.135
dos alts gevezn di,

00:02:50.208 --> 00:02:53.324
vos me hot tsuzamengenumen di yidn dar- dort, dafke fun di gegnt.

00:02:53.701 --> 00:02:56.778
dos iz geven demoltstn vos far a land?

00:02:56.833 --> 00:02:59.222
dos iz gevezn in der Kongres Poyln.

00:03:00.367 --> 00:03:05.187
velkhe, kent ir mir zogn genoy dem, di genoye date fun ayer geburts-TAG?

00:03:05.665 --> 00:03:08.562
ikh bin geboyrn gevorn dem ershtn, loyt vi ikh,

00:03:08.838 --> 00:03:12.798
loyt vi me hot mir oyfgegebn. keyn genoye date veys ikh nisht

00:03:12.922 --> 00:03:15.332
tsi se iz rikhtik. ober

00:03:15.332 --> 00:03:16.665
dos vos ikh veys,

00:03:16.665 --> 00:03:18.164
dem ershtn yuni,

00:03:18.490 --> 00:03:20.341
nayntsn finef un tsvontsik.

00:03:27.991 --> 00:03:30.393
vi hot geheysn ayer foter?

00:03:30.387 --> 00:03:32.154
mayn foter hot geheysn Yitskhok,

00:03:33.762 --> 00:03:34.671
di muter,

00:03:34.671 --> 00:03:35.529
Khaye.

00:03:36.783 --> 00:03:39.882
ikh hob gehat a, ikh bin gevezn di eyntsikste fun di familye.

00:03:40.192 --> 00:03:41.992
ikh hob gehat yingere shvester

00:03:42.571 --> 00:03:44.169
un nokh a yingern bruder.

00:03:45.879 --> 00:03:50.311
der foter, fun ve- velkhn yorgang iz geven der foter, gedenkt ir?

00:03:49.034 --> 00:03:53.450
mayn foter i- iz gevezn a nayntsn, akhtsn finef un nayntsik.

00:03:54.215 --> 00:03:57.264
un oykh geven a geboyrener i- fun Poyln?

00:03:57.455 --> 00:04:01.330
a geboyrener fun Poyln, ober er hot ⟨zikh⟩ geboyrn in Apt, in OPATOW

00:04:01.488 --> 00:04:03.339
bin ikh nisht hundert protsent zikher.

00:04:03.429 --> 00:04:06.106
un di mame fun di velkhn yorgang iz zi geven?

00:04:05.200 --> 00:04:06.590
di mame iz naynts-

00:04:06.590 --> 00:04:09.594
oyb ikh hob nisht keyn toes, oyb ikh gedenk rikhtik,

00:04:09.622 --> 00:04:11.694
vayl mir hobn gekrign a bukh

00:04:11.714 --> 00:04:13.936
fun nayntsn fertsik,

00:04:14.110 --> 00:04:15.134
fun Poyln,

00:04:15.190 --> 00:04:20.208
mit di ale resh- mit di ale nemen fun yidn vos zenen geblibn, vos hobn zikh gefinen in nayntsn fertsik

00:04:20.253 --> 00:04:21.440
in OPATOW.

00:04:21.485 --> 00:04:24.500
iz dakht zikh mir dortn opgegebn az naytsn tsvey.

00:04:27.745 --> 00:04:35.030
ir hot mir gezogt frier, ir hot gehat a brud- a shvester un a bru- a yingere shvester un a bruder. vi hot geheysn di shvester?

00:04:34.225 --> 00:04:36.025
di shvester hot geheysn Feyge,

00:04:35.845 --> 00:04:38.455
un ven iz zi geven geboyrn gevorn, velkhe yor?

00:04:37.634 --> 00:04:42.859
di Fe- iz geboyrn gevorn zi- nayntsn zibn un tsvontsik, denk ikh.

00:04:42.174 --> 00:04:43.484
un der bruder?

00:04:44.080 --> 00:04:45.222
hot geheysn

00:04:44.086 --> 00:04:46.136
iz gevezn, Moyshe,

00:04:46.136 --> 00:04:47.551
un er iz geboyrn gevorn

00:04:49.362 --> 00:04:51.840
bay nayntsn draysik, oder eyn un draysik.

00:04:51.840 --> 00:04:54.025
ge- di genoy fun gedenk ikh nisht,

00:04:54.025 --> 00:04:55.468
dos muz ikh shoyn nokhkukn,

00:04:55.468 --> 00:05:00.416
ober umgefer, der datum sh- zenen umgefer rikhtik.

00:05:00.196 --> 00:05:02.100
zayt zhe azoy gut,

00:05:02.100 --> 00:05:08.139
azoy vi ir hot mir dertseylt di perzenlekhe informatsye vegn aykh un vegn ayer mishpokhe,

00:05:08.431 --> 00:05:13.353
oyb ir volt mir gekent dertseyln, vos gedenkt ir als yingele nokh,

00:05:13.460 --> 00:05:15.479
fun ayer yugntvarg

00:05:16.278 --> 00:05:17.470
se iz

00:05:16.295 --> 00:05:20.592
in OPATOW. vi hot zikh gelebt? dertseylt mir a bisl vegn di mishpokhe, vegn alemen.

00:05:19.231 --> 00:05:20.120
mishpokhes.

00:05:20.311 --> 00:05:22.617
se iz azoy. mayn foter iz gevezn a shnayder.

00:05:23.754 --> 00:05:25.438
mir hobn gearbet in der heym.

00:05:25.475 --> 00:05:27.691
gehaltn a gezel. veyst vos heyst a gezel,

00:05:27.702 --> 00:05:29.688
a gehilf, fun shnayder-gehilf.

00:05:30.504 --> 00:05:33.384
di meynstn arbet, hot er gearbet far

00:05:33.777 --> 00:05:35.746
goyim in di derfer arum.

00:05:36.528 --> 00:05:39.189
er iz gevezn dafke, zeyer a gute balmelokhe.

00:05:40.122 --> 00:05:47.187
un keyn groyse glikn iz in der heym nisht gevezn. me iz, mir hobn koym ekzistirt, koym gemakht a

00:05:47.345 --> 00:05:48.352
parnose.

00:05:48.982 --> 00:05:51.845
dos lebn iz gevezn loyt vi ikh farshtey,

00:05:52.019 --> 00:05:53.988
mir hot zikh oysgezen az Apt

00:05:54.145 --> 00:05:56.277
iz der, iz der ⟨nopl⟩ fun der velt.

00:05:56.305 --> 00:05:57.948
az keyn gresers iz nishto

00:05:57.948 --> 00:05:58.713
fun Apt.

00:05:59.073 --> 00:06:00.521
als kleyn kind,

00:06:00.521 --> 00:06:02.729
bi- koydem kol bin ikh gegangen in di shule,

00:06:03.545 --> 00:06:05.210
in di folkshule.

00:06:07.426 --> 00:06:11.600
dos iz gevezn a halbn tog umgefer, efsher epes mer vi a halbn tog.

00:06:11.600 --> 00:06:14.154
un der andern halbn tog bin ikh gegangen in kheyder.

00:06:14.311 --> 00:06:17.934
ober geendikt, ge- oyfgehert dem kheyder zeyer yung,

00:06:18.884 --> 00:06:23.013
vayl ikh hob badorfn zikh avekzetsn, helfn di mishpokhe mit arbet.

00:06:24.571 --> 00:06:29.155
un di shule hob ikh bloyz geendikt di UNK shule, dos heyst zibn klasn.

00:06:30.005 --> 00:06:32.069
se iz keyn, keyn,

00:06:32.069 --> 00:06:34.778
oyb, ikh gedenk nisht oyb se iz gevezn bay undz a,

00:06:34.778 --> 00:06:35.922
a hekhere

00:06:36.552 --> 00:06:38.605
shulung, vayle oyb,

00:06:38.982 --> 00:06:41.744
ikh gedenk az me hot badorfn forn in an andere shtot arayn.

00:06:42.408 --> 00:06:44.191
yo, a gimnazye iz yo gevezn.

00:06:44.281 --> 00:06:46.320
yo a gimnazye, yo yetst derman ikh zikh,

00:06:46.320 --> 00:06:47.802
se iz gevezn a gimnazye.

00:06:48.280 --> 00:06:54.569
ober leyder ikh hob nisht, me hot nisht, koydem kol hot men nisht yedn eynem opgenumen, ongenumen, se iz tsulib di,

00:06:55.891 --> 00:06:57.323
un azoy az,

00:06:57.323 --> 00:06:59.446
ikh hob gemuzt zikh avekzetsn arbetn.

00:06:59.840 --> 00:07:03.682
bay elef yor hob ikh, elef oder tsvelef hob ikh sh-, iz men shoyn gezitsn un gearbet,

00:07:03.957 --> 00:07:07.765
geholfn dem tatn mit, mitn, baym, baym varshtat.

00:07:08.632 --> 00:07:09.807
un,

00:07:10.049 --> 00:07:13.672
un azoy es, bay u- mir hobn gehat a, a ruik lebn,

00:07:15.179 --> 00:07:17.604
parnose, tsu fil parnose iz nisht gevezn.

00:07:17.879 --> 00:07:19.578
se iz koym, koym gevezn.

00:07:20.934 --> 00:07:30.294
yetst volt ikh aykh gevolt fregn, dermant zikh a bisl vegn di shkole, ve- vegn di shule yorn. vi hot oysgezen dos, i- ir hot zikh gelernt in a shule,

00:07:26.264 --> 00:07:27.764
yo di sh-

00:07:29.540 --> 00:07:32.757
shule, yo. di shule yorn zenen geven zeyer, zeyer shvere.

00:07:33.202 --> 00:07:34.512
vos heyst shvere?

00:07:35.362 --> 00:07:39.119
dos, dos gedenk ikh genoy. di polyakn hobn undz opgetun groyse tsores.

00:07:39.715 --> 00:07:44.789
shtelt aykh for az me iz aroysgegangen, a- az me hot gehat a HAFSAKA, iberrays fun sho tsu sho,

00:07:45.132 --> 00:07:50.037
ot, zenen di tsvey dray yidn vos zenen geven bay undz in klas hobn moyre gehat aroystsugeyn in droysn,

00:07:50.127 --> 00:07:52.889
vayl zey ⟨hobn⟩ di YUDN, di polyakn hobn undz mamesh geshlogn.

00:07:53.874 --> 00:07:57.007
se iz gevezn an opkumenish dos geyn yedn tog in shule arayn.

00:07:57.130 --> 00:07:58.587
az me iz aheymge- s-

00:07:58.587 --> 00:08:03.810
tsum bayshpil, me hot geendikt dem sezon, az me, me hot gevust az mir zenen fray far etlekhe vokhn,

00:08:03.810 --> 00:08:05.709
iz bay undz gevezn a groyse simkhe,

00:08:05.754 --> 00:08:07.126
az me hot nisht badorfn

00:08:07.126 --> 00:08:07.911
geyn in shule.

00:08:07.911 --> 00:08:11.041
