tsi hot ir gefilt oykh antisemitizm fun di zayt fun di lerer?

00:08:22.494 --> 00:08:23.233
yo.

00:08:23.270 --> 00:08:23.872
yo.

00:08:23.709 --> 00:08:25.374
ir gedenkt epes a fal?

00:08:24.063 --> 00:08:25.441
me hot er gefil-

