00:08:35.875 --> 00:08:38.007
demolt hot men nokh gemegt

00:08:38.007 --> 00:08:39.684
bashtrofn a shiler,

00:08:39.740 --> 00:08:41.332
tsum bayshpil me hot gegebn der hant

00:08:41.360 --> 00:08:43.362
mit a LINIJKA, mit a,

00:08:43.486 --> 00:08:47.159
az me hot es, se hot gants gut, gants shtark vey getun. me hot es gut gefilt.

00:08:47.789 --> 00:08:49.539
far mamesh a kleynikeyt.

00:08:50.574 --> 00:08:53.049
in algemeyn iz di, di,

00:08:53.560 --> 00:08:58.600
se, me hot nisht, d- dos lernen aleyn iz geven an opkumenish. se iz nisht geven keyn fargenign tsum lernen.

00:08:58.775 --> 00:09:02.094
se iz, se iz gevezn a shvere, shvere tsayt far undz lernen, yidn.

00:09:02.825 --> 00:09:05.182
yedn fals, dos gedenk ikh bay undz in shtot.

00:09:05.238 --> 00:09:08.517
vi azoy iz gevezn in andere shtetlekh veys ikh nisht, vayl ikh bin geven a kleyn kind.

00:09:08.517 --> 00:09:10.953
mir zenen kimat nisht aroysgeforn fun shtetl.

00:09:12.393 --> 00:09:14.834
vos gedenkt ir vegn,

00:09:14.958 --> 00:09:19.576
vi hot zikh gefirt dos yidishe lebn in OPATOW? se iz geven a sakh yidn in OPATOW?

00:09:19.362 --> 00:09:24.169
OPATOW hot zikh getseylt, se, OPATOW hot zikh gerekhnt far eyner fun di

00:09:24.169 --> 00:09:27.879
yidishe shtetlekh in dem gegnt fun Poyln.

00:09:28.036 --> 00:09:29.819
se hot geheysn a yidishe shtot.

00:09:30.483 --> 00:09:33.262
genoy, vifl yidn se hobn gelebt

00:09:33.622 --> 00:09:35.171
iz zenen opgegebn,

00:09:35.208 --> 00:09:38.530
loyt vi ikh hob arayngekukt in dem bukh, zenen opgegebn

00:09:38.566 --> 00:09:41.328
etlekhene tsifern, eyner zogt zeks toyznt,

00:09:41.620 --> 00:09:44.382
eyner zogt zibn toyznt, un eyner zogt akht toyznt.

00:09:44.590 --> 00:09:47.909
se iz geven, me ken zogn, tsvishn ⟨azoy⟩ finef un ⟨azoy⟩ akht toyznt yidn.

00:09:50.142 --> 00:09:51.740
se iz gevezn,

00:09:51.830 --> 00:09:56.397
ales iz gevezn in dem shtetl, farshidene grupirungen, farshidene organizatsyes,

00:09:56.454 --> 00:09:58.130
farshidene khevres,

00:09:58.175 --> 00:10:00.903
ales vos a groyse shtot hot, ober in minyatur.

00:10:01.769 --> 00:10:06.795
mir hobn, ikh hob tsum bayshpil nisht gehert tsu keyn shum organizatsye, vayl,

00:10:06.795 --> 00:10:08.446
ershtns bin ikh geven tsu yung,

00:10:08.502 --> 00:10:11.056
ikh ho'mir gehat mayn svive, mayne khaveyrim,

00:10:11.101 --> 00:10:13.525
di fraye tsayt in ovnt hobn mir farbrakht

00:10:13.801 --> 00:10:18.115
mit leyenen epes, oder stam redn politik,

00:10:18.610 --> 00:10:24.039
se iz nisht a hayntike, se iz nisht azoy vi di hayntike yugnt gevezn. se iz geven an andere atmosfere, an andere tsayt.

00:10:25.225 --> 00:10:30.867
un m- undz zenen gevezn zeyer tsufridn. m- mir als kinder hobn nisht gefilt d- dem druk fun di,

00:10:30.867 --> 00:10:31.897
fun di

00:10:31.897 --> 00:10:32.859
parnose.

00:10:32.859 --> 00:10:35.834
dos hot getrogn, vayzt oys, der tate, mit di, mi di familye.

00:10:36.093 --> 00:10:39.445
azoy az mir hobn gefilt tsufridn als yinglekh.

00:10:39.789 --> 00:10:45.959
ober leyder hot zikh di kindheyt, undz ho'mir kimat keyn yugnt nisht gehat. zeyer yung hot men undz fartribn in der lager.

00:10:46.404 --> 00:10:47.832
azoy az,

00:10:48.479 --> 00:10:50.583
ikh volt aykh nokh gevolt fregn,

00:10:50.859 --> 00:10:52.484
redndik vegn

00:10:52.484 --> 00:10:55.224
yudntum vos hot gelebt in ayer shtot

00:10:55.449 --> 00:10:56.928
far der milkhome,

00:10:57.339 --> 00:11:01.434
hot ir dermant farshidene organizatsyes. velkhe organizatsyes?

00:11:00.984 --> 00:11:03.976
se iz gevezn al, se iz gevezn tsienistishe organizatsyes.

00:11:03.987 --> 00:11:05.804
se iz gevezn Habeytar,

00:11:05.928 --> 00:11:07.053
gedenk ikh.

00:11:07.227 --> 00:11:10.394
se iz gevezn Hakhaluts Hatsair iz gevezn.

00:11:11.007 --> 00:11:14.751
ikh gedenk afile in velkhe, in velkhe gebaydes zenen ⟨mir⟩ gevezn. undz hobn,

00:11:14.770 --> 00:11:19.392
vayl ven ikh bin ikh gegangen in shul arayn, a tsayt bin ikh gegangen in shul arayn vayl di shul iz gevezn nisht vayt

00:11:19.392 --> 00:11:20.604
fun undzer hoyz.

00:11:20.879 --> 00:11:23.821
ober me hot undz ibergetrogn an andere shul, in a naye,

00:11:23.821 --> 00:11:26.223
vos mir ho'mir badorfn geyn zeyer, zeyer vayt.

00:11:26.347 --> 00:11:29.227
se hot genumen kimat a sho geyn in di shul arayn.

00:11:29.334 --> 00:11:31.825
bin ikh adurkhgegangen nokh dem hoyz ven se iz gevezn

00:11:32.050 --> 00:11:34.385
di, ven se iz geshtanen dortn di Khaluts Hatsair.

00:11:34.396 --> 00:11:37.428
un kh- der Beytar dafke gevezn lebn di shule

00:11:37.501 --> 00:11:39.672
