se iz gevezn,

00:12:00.721 --> 00:12:03.477
a sakh hob ikh shoyn dermant, Bney Akiva,

00:12:05.041 --> 00:12:09.507
se, se iz ober gevezn kimat ale organizatsyes vos iz gevezn in andere shtet.

00:12:10.610 --> 00:12:14.097
yetst volt ikh aykh mit ayer erloybenish gefregt nokh a frage,

00:12:14.761 --> 00:12:18.485
vi iz geven dos religyeze lebn bay aykh in shtub?

00:12:19.233 --> 00:12:21.067
bay undz in shtub iz azoy

