ho- se, hobn zikh geklibn arum im,

00:23:12.110 --> 00:23:14.129
hobn mir gevust az mir zenen bashitst.

00:23:14.422 --> 00:23:15.327
vayl er hot,

00:23:15.485 --> 00:23:16.773
er hot zikh nisht gelozt.

00:23:16.801 --> 00:23:20.216
un se iz geven a sakh feler, a sakh mol, ven er hot zey mamesh tseshlogn di polyakn.

00:23:20.227 --> 00:23:23.950
azoy ale, durkh ale tsayt zenen gevezn geshlegn tsvishn,

00:23:24.074 --> 00:23:27.359
tsum bayshpil, nokh, ir dermant mikh. yetst derman ikh zikh vayter.

00:23:27.567 --> 00:23:32.050
se iz gevezn bay undz, un vu zenen mir geganen shpatsirn, a shabes, a yonte- a yontev?

00:23:32.259 --> 00:23:34.970
se iz gevezn, se hot geheysn Hintern CMENTARZ.

00:23:35.229 --> 00:23:36.877
vos heyst Hintern CMENTARZ?

00:23:37.135 --> 00:23:38.466
se iz geven a poylishe,

00:23:38.466 --> 00:23:40.404
BET HAKVA- BET HAKVAROT,

00:23:38.527 --> 00:23:39.472
beys hakvores

00:23:40.544 --> 00:23:43.478
un dortn ze'mir aroyfgeganen, se iz geven a barg aroyf,

00:23:43.478 --> 00:23:46.799
un dortn geven a vaser, se iz geven lonkes,

00:23:47.362 --> 00:23:51.417
un yidn hobn zikh ongehoybn dortn a bisl, gevolt toyvlen, yinglekh, kleyne.

00:23:51.417 --> 00:23:56.013
azoy vi zey hobn ge- di polyakn hobn gezen, di shkotsimlekh, hobn gezen az me tut zikh oys,

00:23:56.137 --> 00:23:57.602
hobn zey genumen di hint,

00:23:57.602 --> 00:23:59.320
zey hobn ongehoybn nokhtsuyogn, zey hobn a,

00:23:59.529 --> 00:24:01.632
mamesh antlofn naketdikerheyt.

00:24:01.722 --> 00:24:03.370
azoy hobn zey alem opgemakht.

00:24:04.119 --> 00:24:08.619
un mir zenen undz ongefaln, tomer mir zenen nor aroysgeganen fun di shtot,

00:24:08.979 --> 00:24:10.644
flegn zey undz onfaln,

00:24:10.750 --> 00:24:13.161
di polyakn mamesh fun di derfer UNK,

00:24:13.180 --> 00:24:15.402
nisht di alte, nor di yingere.

00:24:15.796 --> 00:24:19.520
vorshaynlekh az dos iz shoyn gevezn gelernt fun der heym az me darf azoy tun.

00:24:20.116 --> 00:24:26.371
azoy se zenen ale mol gevezn feler fun antisemitishe oysbrukhn avantures un,

00:24:26.579 --> 00:24:27.907
dort a gantse tsayt.

00:24:28.267 --> 00:24:31.754
yetst volt ikh aykh gevolt fregn nokh a frage vegn ayer shtot.

00:24:32.992 --> 00:24:36.788
se iz geven dortn shuln, rabonim, ir dermant zikh epes, v-

00:24:35.478 --> 00:24:38.150
yo, se se. se iz geven zeyer a, koydem kol

00:24:38.982 --> 00:24:43.044
Apt iz a shtot fun, a historishe shtot fun rabonim.

00:24:43.235 --> 00:24:44.776
fun di dinastye fun,

00:24:44.821 --> 00:24:47.043
koydem kol iz, Apt hot aroysgegebn

00:24:47.302 --> 00:24:48.916
dem groysn rebn,

00:24:49.225 --> 00:24:53.577
Av- Avrom Yeshue Heshl, dos hot, er hot geheysn der Apter.

00:24:53.577 --> 00:24:55.787
in di yidishe velt, vem ir vet fregn,

00:24:55.790 --> 00:24:58.231
der Apter, vet men a, vet men visn ver dos iz.

00:24:58.456 --> 00:24:59.952
iz gevezn a groyser rebe.

00:25:00.279 --> 00:25:03.086
un se iz gevezn afile der Kozhnitser rebe,

00:25:03.097 --> 00:25:04.407
di eltern zayne,

00:25:05.459 --> 00:25:07.794
der der foter hot geheysn Shabse Aynbinder.

00:25:07.794 --> 00:25:08.879
shtamt fun a,

00:25:09.155 --> 00:25:11.799
se iz geven, dafke in dem bukh iz do a gantse,

00:25:12.378 --> 00:25:14.147
a groyse teyl fun dem bukh zenen

00:25:14.147 --> 00:25:15.607
ibergeshribn di gantse,

00:25:15.607 --> 00:25:18.599
koy- yo, se iz gevezn oykhet a Yekhezkel Landoy,

00:25:18.723 --> 00:25:21.856
zeyer a barimter rebe, er iz gevezn nakher rov in Prag.

00:25:23.094 --> 00:25:24.542
se iz a, a,

00:25:24.542 --> 00:25:27.495
zeyer bavuste in di yidishe velt, in di,

00:25:27.532 --> 00:25:28.842
in der religyeze velt.

00:25:29.337 --> 00:25:33.500
yetst iz gevezn a oyel oyfn BET HAKVAROT fun groyse rabonim.

00:25:33.624 --> 00:25:36.453
gedenk der rebe reb Meyerl, groyser rebe,

00:25:36.526 --> 00:25:38.354
yedn yortsayt,

00:25:38.354 --> 00:25:40.030
es iz oysgekumen der yor- der yortsayt,

00:25:40.171 --> 00:25:41.364
zenen gekumen

00:25:41.437 --> 00:25:42.899
fun arum un arum

00:25:43.293 --> 00:25:45.121
yidn, kalikes,

00:25:45.121 --> 00:25:48.007
a- alte un kranke, betn mit kvitlekh.

00:25:48.007 --> 00:25:49.998
ikh gedenk als kleyn yingl,

00:25:50.026 --> 00:25:52.771
ikh hob ⟨geven⟩ arayngekukt in dem oyel iz gevezn ongeleygt

00:25:53.232 --> 00:25:55.944
fil fil der gantse dos iz geven helft mit kvitlekh.

00:25:56.759 --> 00:26:00.466
un demolt far di oremelayt iz oykh geven a yontev dafke.

00:26:00.775 --> 00:26:03.000
vayl me hot gegebn tsdoke.

00:26:03.000 --> 00:26:04.567
dos iz gevezn eyn mol,

00:26:04.623 --> 00:26:07.574
ikh denk az dos iz gevezn in, in ov.

00:26:07.574 --> 00:26:08.735
in khoydesh ov.

00:26:09.753 --> 00:26:13.547
se iz gevezn, hot geven a raykhe BET HAKVAROT in Poyln,

00:26:13.550 --> 00:26:15.063
in bay undz in Apt.

00:26:15.541 --> 00:26:19.164
matseyves zenen gevezn zeyer zeyer alt, mistam etlekhe hundert yor.

00:26:19.608 --> 00:26:21.040
se iz gevezn a shul,

00:26:21.040 --> 00:26:22.640
zeyer a prekhtike shul,

00:26:22.899 --> 00:26:24.457
zeyer a bavuste shul,

00:26:24.457 --> 00:26:26.572
di shul loyt,

00:26:27.084 --> 00:26:30.453
loyt vi me dertseylt, iz alt gevezn zibn hundert yor.

00:26:31.201 --> 00:26:35.566
in lebn der shul iz geshtanen a beys hamedresh, vos me zogt az se nokh efsher elter vi der shul.

00:26:36.230 --> 00:26:39.279
di sh- di di fentster fun der beys hamedresh

00:26:39.436 --> 00:26:41.624
zenen gevezn mamesh glaykh mit der erd.

00:26:41.697 --> 00:26:47.176
dos zogt men fun dem vos hobn z- der der beys hamedresh hot zikh langzam langzam ⟨aropgerukt⟩, arayngezetst.

00:26:47.418 --> 00:26:50.073
vayl ikh ken mir nisht forshteln me zol boyen a beys hamedresh

00:26:50.073 --> 00:26:52.053
mit fentster glaykh tsu der erd.

00:26:52.565 --> 00:26:55.428
dos iz mamesh a a fakt, az der erd,

00:26:55.855 --> 00:26:59.455
me hot arayngeganen in beys hamedresh ze'mir arayngeganen glaykh in durkhn, durkhn fentster.

00:26:59.455 --> 00:27:01.267
in inevey- un se iz geven tif untn.

00:27:02.572 --> 00:27:05.218
un nakher iz gevezn nokh etlekhe bote-midroshim,

00:27:05.218 --> 00:27:08.416
vayl se iz dokh geven a yidish shtetl, se,

00:27:08.416 --> 00:27:11.695
az se hot tsum bayshpil eyner mekhalel shabes geven befarhesye,

00:27:11.836 --> 00:27:13.518
hot dos gantse shtetl gevust.

00:27:17.067 --> 00:27:19.610
vos nokh ken ikh aykh zogn vegn Apt

00:27:19.902 --> 00:27:24.742
ir kent zikh dermnanen efsher epes bavuse perzenlekhkeytn fun Apt?

00:27:24.745 --> 00:27:26.967
fun fun ayer tsayt vos zenen geven?

00:27:26.517 --> 00:27:28.385
perzenlekhkeytn in Apt,

00:27:29.707 --> 00:27:34.527
zenen kimat nisht gevezn. zenen, se iz gevezn epes eyn shrayber,

00:27:34.803 --> 00:27:41.227
vos, koydem kol er iz o- er iz oykhet Perets, Yitskhok Leybish Perets, iz gevezn an Apter eydem.

00:27:42.127 --> 00:27:44.782
azoy az mir zenen shtoltsirn a bisl mit.

00:27:44.782 --> 00:27:48.247
kho- khotsh nisht direkt, ober a bisl a, iz es a,

00:27:48.337 --> 00:27:51.250
er flegt bashraybn zayne bashraybungen, flegt er dermanen Apt.

00:27:52.285 --> 00:27:54.401
un keyn spetsyele

00:27:54.401 --> 00:27:58.945
groyse mentshn iz iz in Apt nisht gevezn, akhuts fun tsvishn undz aleyn

00:27:59.137 --> 00:28:00.717
vos groyse mentshn,

00:28:02.680 --> 00:28:05.459
groyse mentshn vos zenen gevorn nakher barimt

00:28:05.532 --> 00:28:06.978
zenen kimat nisht gevezn.

00:28:07.355 --> 00:28:08.834
yedn fals, ikh gedenk nisht.

00:28:09.481 --> 00:28:11.974
efsher zenen gevezn eynike ober ikh gedenk nisht.

00:28:13.396 --> 00:28:18.724
yetst mit ayer erloybenish veln mir do iberraysn. me vet toyshn a kaset un mir veln onfangen vayter.
